foia:ProcessedAppealSection.foia:FootnoteText: Concerning all tables in Section VI, not all components process administrative appeals. OSD/JS FOIA Appeals Branch processes the following components’ appeals: AFRICOM, CENTCOM, DoDEA, DTIC, EUCOM, JPRA, NGB, NORTHCOM, OSD/JS, PACOM, SOCOM, SOUTHCOM, STRATCOM, TRANSCOM, and TMA.
